---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import AboutHero from "../components/AboutHero.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import rominaWilmot from "../assets/romina-with-heart.webp";
import ContactForm from "../components/ContactForm.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="flex-grow">
    <AboutHero />

    <!-- Our Mission Section -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container py-24">
      <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">
            She has lived firsthand the same challenges she is trying to help
            solve...
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              Romina is passionate about connecting families with resources that
              make their lives better. Her family encountered similar challenges
              moving to a new place with limited language skills. Originally
              from Honduras and growing up in the City of Boston she overcame
              many challenges. This has been the deeper driver of her behavior.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              Starting her career in retail developing and executing national
              marketing strategies for Fortune 500 companies supporting brands
              like Marshalls/TJMaxx and Staples, Inc. Romina found her calling
              for promoting products and services to improve people’s lives and
              wellbeing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-body leading-relaxed">
              That was the moment when she transitioned into community health
              care. By combining her vast experience in marketing, branding, and
              business development with community health and wellness initiative
              that engage diverse and vulnerable communities, she developed a
              methodology for immediate impact for all organizations involved in
              the healthcare process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-8 mt-8 lg:mt-24 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 space-y-4"
          >
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Romina’s proprietary strategy has been used to strengthen referral
              programs, local branding, and social media presence that promote
              specifically to ethnically diverse and hard-to-reach audiences.
              Through producing and hosting her own TV Shows to promote local
              health awareness campaigns, Romina has built a brand that can be
              leveraged for the good of the community overall, as well as
              developed the expertise in video production which has been found
              to increasingly enhance communication to bilingual healthcare
              consumers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-200 p-8 rounded-2xl space-y-4">
            <p class="font-body text-lg italic text-slate-700">
              "Ready to expand your possibilities of what you can accomplish?
              Contact Romina Wilmot below for a meet & greet at your workplace
              or somewhere in the community."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Values Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
          <div
            class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-black/80"
          >
            <Image
              alt="Romina Wilmot"
              class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover"
              src={rominaWilmot}
            />
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-secondary-fixed-dim mb-6">
              Engaging with heart
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-100 mb-4">
              There are many challenges in healthcare communication between
              well-meaning organizations, providers and end consumers in your
              community right now.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-100 mb-4">
              Providers are now tasked to provide high quality health care at a
              low cost to populations who are very diverse and face social and
              chronic issues, in addition to dealing with low health literacy.
            </p>

            <p class="text-slate-100 mb-4">
              Organizations need to be equipped with the most effective strategies to grow and make a positive impact on the health outcomes of the communities they serve.
            </p>

            <p class="text-slate-100 mb-4">
            They need to engage with heart.
            </p>

            <button class="bg-white text-primary px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/RW-Consulting-LLC-872108586497713" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                Let's connect on Facebook
              </a>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ContactForm />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
